    "Ethical considerations: AI algorithms may inadvertently perpetuate biases present in historical data.",
    "For example, if a dataset primarily includes data from a specific demographic group, the AI model may not generalize well to other populations.",
    "Thus, researchers must be cautious about potential biases and ensure that ethical guidelines are followed during data collection and model training.",
